		    <hr />
		    <p><a href="files/200911-IS-NSF-survey3.pdf"><strong>Internet2 Campus Connectivity Survey</strong></a></p>
<p>At the request of the NSF, Internet2 issued an electronic survey in October, 2009, to its research university members inquiring about the current level of connectivity they have to the commercial Internet and research networks like Internet2. The <a href="files/200911-IS-NSF-survey3.pdf">survey results <em>(pdf)</em></a> helped to inform the FCC's National Broadband plan development.</p>
